  "notes": [
    "This study compares two genomic profiling approaches in sarcoma patients using real-world data from Japan's nationwide database",
    "GenMine TOP is a dual DNA-RNA panel with tumor-normal matching, while FoundationOne CDx is a DNA-only tumor panel",
    "The study demonstrates superior fusion gene detection with RNA-based analysis compared to DNA-only approaches",
    "Germline pathogenic variants can only be detected with tumor-normal matched testing, not with tumor-only panels"
  ]
